      "updated": 1783605209229,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "! multiple species (markers set) per kit/library are not allowed.\n If you have more than one species per library, run the pipeline twice.\n\n- Limited number of the queries per kit - when the kit status \"analysed\", user can reanalyse it only\nafter admin approval \n\n-Very important to check for all species: sex reference have to be formatted as in UA_primers X:seq/Y:seq\n\n- FASTQ files are deleted from the storage in 2 weeks. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "! multiple species (markers set) per kit/library are not allowed.\n If you have more than one species per library, run the pipeline twice.\n\n- Limited number of the queries per kit - when the kit status \"analysed\", user can reanalyse it only\nafter admin approval \n\n-Very important to check for all species: sex reference have to be formatted as in UA_primers X:seq/Y:seq\n\n- FASTQ files are deleted from the storage in 2 weeks. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
